Package general.entities

Class Organization

java.lang.Object
general.entities.Organization
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Organization>
public class Organization extends Object implements Comparable<Organization>, Serializable
Entity of organization. Contains getter of each field. Restrictions on fields: id must be greater than 0, must be unique, set automatic, name cannot be null or empty, coordinates cannot be null, creationDate cannot be null, set automatic, annualTurnover cannot be null, must be greater than 0, fullName cannot be null, employeesCount must be greater than 0, organizationType cannot be null, postalAddress cannot be null
Since:
1.0
Author:
safarislava
